    public static class CEPEngine.CEPEngineBuilder
extends java.lang.Object
    Builder class for the CEPEngine.

    Use a dedicated CEPEngine.CEPEngineBuilder for every CEPEngine to be created, or make sure the rules assigned to the builder do not interfere among multiple engines.
